Hello! The previous hints are very accurate. To get 100 points, always use the 'filter' for liquids/gases and the 'vial' for solids. You can only combine two items at a time, and they must both be processed by the *same* tool (e.g., two 'vialed' items, or two 'filtered' items). The 100-point recipes I found are:
1. Filter & Honey (e.g., filtered honey nectar) + Filter & Ghostly Vapor (e.g., filtered kraken ink or filtered dragon's breath) = 100 points.
2. Vial & Sunstone (e.g., sunstone extract) + Vial & Dandelion (e.g., obsidian extract or mushroom extract) = 100 points.
3. Vial & Unicorn Horn (e.g., magical dragon scale extract) + Vial & Obsidian (e.g., obsidian extract or mushroom extract) = 100 points.
Prioritize making these pairs as soon as you have the ingredients and tools. Good luck!

message: Use the Vial tool for solid ingredients, and the Filter tool for gas or liquid ingredients. To combine items, always mix only two items, and they must both have been processed by the same type of tool (e.g., two 'vial' items or two 'filter' items).
